OL,3,CWoman could face murder trial over
OL,4,Cdeath of pensioner on Christmas Day
OL,6,FA woman charged with murdering a
OL,7,Fpensioner on Christmas Day has had a
OL,8,Fprovisional trial date set.
OL,10,FStefania Glowka, 63, is accused of
OL,11,Fkilling Tamara Glowka, who was in her
OL,12,F80s.
OL,14,FDuring a hearing at Bristol Crown
OL,15,FCourt on Wednesday, at which Glowka
OL,16,Fwas not required to appear, she was
OL,17,Fremanded in custody.
