OL,3,CWoman could face murder trial over
OL,4,Cdeath of pensioner on Christmas Day
OL,6,FGlowka, a Polish national, is next due
OL,7,Fto appear in court on 20 March 2026
OL,8,Fand a provisional trial date has been
OL,9,Fset for 1 June 2026. She has not
OL,10,Fentered a plea.
OL,12,FPolice were called to reports of an
OL,13,Fassault on Christmas morning at a flat
OL,14,Fin Keepers Road, Devizes, Wiltshire.
OL,16,FTamara Glowka was later declared dead
OL,17,Fat the scene.
OL,19,FMs Glowka, who was known to the
OL,20,Fdefendant, was identified from
OL,21,Fpublicly available court papers.
